song.englishname: Great And Mighty Is Our God

english.segment1: Great and mighty is our God (Halleluiah, yes you are God). Great and mighty is our God (There's nobody like Jesus anywhere). Great and mighty is our God (Nobody like the Lord, Nobody like the Lord) {x2}. Great and mighty is our God (No, No, No, No) {X2}. Great and mighty is our God (He's a mighty God). He's a mighty God (Repeat till fade).
